---
title: Bacon-Wrapped Pesto and Cheese-Stuffed Turkey with Roasted Potatoes
description: Stuffed turkey is a classic dinner for good reason! Hearty turkey gets a major upgrade when stuffed with a creamy, cheesy filling that is boosted with tangy red pepper pesto, then wrapped in smoky, savoury bacon.
